title: Duck filo baskets
ingredients: ['2 duck breasts', '1 chicken breast, cubed', '100g chicken livers', '1 large shallot, minced', '3 tablespoons honey', '2 tablespoons sherry vinegar', '2 oranges, juiced and grated', '30g breadcrumbs', '1 hard boiled egg, peeled and chopped', '2 tablespoons garlic, mashed', '1 tablespoon fresh thyme, leaves only', 'Salt and pepper to taste', '6 filo sheets', '2 tablespoons peanut oil']
